oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Floy Case Collection - tape 1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Various recordings of performances featuring Bill Case and his Melody Boys (performers), Flying X Ranch Boys (performers), Ernest Tubb (performer), and other unidentified performers.
